{"type":null,"faqId":11345,"title":"MATE2(MT2-L05)  手机用不了4G网络，只有3G网络怎么回事？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）目前国内</span><span>4G</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络还在建设中，很多地区没有</span><span>4G</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">信号或者</span><span>4G</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">信号很差，手机不驻留</span><span>4G</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络很正常；</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）确保你用对了卡：各运营商支持的</span><span>4G</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">频段都不一样，</span><span>MT2-L05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机不能使用移动的</span><span>4G</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络，</span><span>MT2-L02/MT2-L01</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不能使用联通的</span><span>4G</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>3) </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">检查</span><span>Settings</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">中的设置：设置</span><span>-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">移动网络</span><span>-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络模式，看看是否选择了</span><span>3G/2G</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">模式；</span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":1,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2105","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398222967000,"seriesProductName":"MT2-L05","visitedTimes":534,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"MATE2(MT2-L05)","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}